00:52:37.830 --> 00:52:40.810
with them, definitely.

00:52:40.810 --> 00:52:44.160
We have a number
of people working

00:52:44.160 --> 00:52:47.670
on some specific technology.

00:52:47.670 --> 00:52:51.770
So we have information
system, but I

00:52:51.770 --> 00:52:57.880
have to say that we're very--
