00:54:33.110 --> 00:54:35.890
So there are so many,
so many different areas

00:54:35.890 --> 00:54:40.350
where we look at possible
technical solutions.

00:54:40.350 --> 00:54:42.840
But in terms of
telecommunication and health

00:54:42.840 --> 00:54:45.040
information system,
